## 4. Data Model

### 4.1. Core Entities

**Users (auth.users)**
- id: uuid (primary key)
- email: string
- role: 'band' | 'fan'
- created_at: timestamp

**Bands (bands)**
- id: uuid (primary key)
- user_id: uuid (foreign key to users)
- name: string
- description: text
- profile_image: string (storage URL)
- created_at: timestamp

**Fans (fans)**
- id: uuid (primary key)
- user_id: uuid (foreign key to users)
- username: string
- profile_image: string (storage URL)
- created_at: timestamp

**Band Subscriptions (band_subscriptions)**
- id: uuid (primary key)
- fan_id: uuid (foreign key to fans)
- band_id: uuid (foreign key to bands)
- created_at: timestamp

